## 14. Experiment submission flow (world-class design)

```
Researcher local UI
  → saves experiment config to saved_experiments (SQLite)
  → clicks "Push to global queue"
  → POST /experiments/submit (with config + description)
  → server sets review_status = 'pending_review'

Server Streamlit admin page
  → shows all pending submissions
  → admin reviews config, can edit/approve/reject
  → on approve: creates job_queue row, notifies researcher (future: email/webhook)
  → on reject: sets review_notes explaining why

Trust tiers (future enhancement):
  → admin can grant 'trusted' status to hw_id
  → trusted researchers → auto_approved (skips review queue)
  → new researchers → always goes through review
```

